The paper proposes a method for motion planning, which is a common topic in robotics (cs.RO). The method involves creating a sequence of roadmaps and using a heuristic to guide the search, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions using the method in difficult environments, which could involve control systems (cs.SY) or computer vision (cs.CV) to perceive the environment.
